&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; naatkal ( english : beautiful days ) is a 2001 comedy tamil film directed by sundar c . the film featured karthik and rambha in the lead roles and became the third collaboration of the pair with sundar after the successes of ullathai allitha ( 1996 ) and unakkaga ellam unakkaga ( 1999 ) . the film also featured mumtaj , goundamani and senthil in pivotal roles and featured music composed by deva . the film released on 7 december 2001 to average reviews from critics . the film is a remake of the malayalam film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film is loosely based on jaishankar movie " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; nee vazhga " .